text = <<ETARGF#binmode?(from ~/.rdoc)------------------------------------------------------------------------------  ARGF.binmode?  -> true or false------------------------------------------------------------------------------  Returns true if +ARGF+ is being read in binary mode; false otherwise. (To  enable binary mode use +ARGF.binmode+.For example:  ARGF.binmode?  #=> false  ARGF.binmode  ARGF.binmode?  #=> true  ET